name: Irises Hammered Gold Bracelet Collection
description: These handmade bracelet on a large 14k gold-filled hammered chain link is accented with a single genuine, hand-cut faceted amethyst or green onyx drop. Lobster clasp, 7.5" long.

name: Vermeil Bracelet Collection
description:
The Vermeil Bracelet collection are handmade beauties that are finished off with a gold vermeil bead accent. Choose from the following gemstones. All bracelets are made of 10mm beads, 7.5" long stretch fit.

Beautiful Camelian has gorgeous red, orange and peach hues that will be a perfect addition to any outfit from casual to dressy. 

Faceted jet black onyx beads will bring out your seductive and mysterious side.

Lose yourself in the bands of varying hues of green of natural malachite. 

Natural palm wood beads of different shapes creates an earthly look
